        <step1>
            <para count="1">After proper preload is achieved, remove end yoke, and install new seal (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1401451">Figure 51</hotlnk>). Apply a small amount of grease on the lip of the sealing
                surface prior to installation.
            </para>
            <figure id="f1401451" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1401451" filename="../figg14/g1401451.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 51. Installing New Seal</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
